-- Hornbach to Grow Without Takeovers, CFO Tells Boersen-Zeitung
-- B y   O l i v e r   S u e s s
-- 2012-02-05T11:56:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-05/hornbach-to-grow-without-takeovers-cfo-tells-boersen-zeitung.html
Hornbach Holding AG (HBH3) , a building
materials and garden supplies retailer, aims to grow without
acquisitions, Chief Financial Officer Roland Pelka said in an
interview with  Boersen-Zeitung .  To contact the reporter on this story:
